data.description: Beautiful Cape Cod home located on the northside of Evansville.  Home is on .38 acres in Brookview Heights subdivision.  Open floor plan and spacious rooms, & a great back yard for entertaining are some of the amenities you will love about this home.  4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths with 2-car attached garage and extra pad for parking.  The yard is great for entertaining with hot tub, above ground pool with deck, and a basketball court 24x38.  The inside layout is open floor plan with living room, den, & family room with brick fireplace.  Family room is open to breakfast nook and kitchen which offers hardwood floors, an abundance of cabinets, and a nice pantry.  Upstairs you will find the 16x14 owner's suite showcasing it's own full bathroom with double vanity and walk-in closet.  There are 3 additional bedrooms plus 2nd spacious full bathroom on upper floor for use.  There is an additional attic storage.  Also included is a shed 8x10 great for storing outdoor items.
